The Telegraph - Calcutta : International

 Blasphemy 

 Paris, Jan. 23 (Reuters): A senior Pakistani official said today that Islamabad planned to reform its blasphemy law that Christian churches and human rights groups say the Muslim majority uses to oppress religious minorities. 




